\begin_layout Standard
For our mass estimates, we assume two different scenarios.
 The first scenario assumes a constant electron density, with the line of
 sight depths based on this assumption.
 The second scenario uses line of sight depths estimated from a combination
 of stellar depth models and galaxy simulations.
